    <dd>personal finance tracker (RIP Mint) <span class="accent">*</span></dd>

    <dt><a href="https://github.com/AlexGaudon/overs.sh">overs.sh</a></dt>
    <dd>file transfer tool over SSH <span class="accent">*</span></dd>

    <dt><a href="https://github.com/AlexGaudon/misery.systems">misery.systems</a></dt>
    <dd>this website <span class="accent">*</span></dd>

    <dt><a href="https://github.com/AlexGaudon/stocky">stocky</a></dt>
    <dd>discord bot for stock prices <span class="accent">*</span></dd>

    <dt><a href="https://github.com/alexgaudon/ntfy-bridge">ntfy-bridge</a></dt>
    <dd>discord to ntfy.sh bridge <span class="accent">*</span></dd>

    <dt><a href="https://github.com/alexgaudon/lootsheet">lootsheet</a></dt>
    <dd>tibia loot splitter <span class="accent">*</span></dd>

    <dt><a href="https://sonarr.tv/">sonarr</a></dt>
    <dd>TV series management</dd>

    <dt><a href="https://radarr.video/">radarr</a></dt>
