    <dt><a href="https://jellyfin.org/">jellyfin</a></dt>
    <dd>media server</dd>

    <dt><a href="https://www.truenas.com/">truenas</a></dt>
    <dd>NAS storage</dd>

    <dt><a href="https://immich.app/">immich</a></dt>
    <dd>photo/video backup</dd>
  </dl>

  <p class="muted"><span class="accent">*</span> = i built it</p>
</Layout>
